                         Angular

                    Bank App in Angular

                    Frond end: Angular
                    Back end: Nodejs(Express)
                    DataBase:MongoDb

    Basic Building Blocks

    1 module - To import 3rd party libraries
    2 component - To create html and css files

          Basic commands   

        1.Create a project- ng new project_name
        2.create a component- ng g c component_name
        3.run-ng serve --open   


        1) Data blinding

        To share data inside the component

        ts-component and html-view

        1.1)one way data binding  (TS to HTML or HTML to TS file)

         a)component to view
              a.1)string interpolation- syntax - {{expression}}

              a.2)Property binding- syntax - [attribute_name]="property"

          b)view to component
            b.1)event binding - syntax - (event_name)="function_name"
            b.2)Event binding using $Event - syntax - (event_name)="function_name($event)"

          